      <title>汇丰银行因交易下滑而裁减亚洲十多名投资银行家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hsbc-cuts-a-dozen-investment-bankers-in-asia-on-deals-slump</link>
